The alleged abduction of three male relatives from Athimba area of Kanuni in Igembe South, Meru County, took a new twist with callers sending families in an harrowing wild goose chase. 

The families of Joseph Giteme, Charles Kalung'e and Bernard Miriti said they had received disturbing calls that their kin could be dead, and could have been the unidentified bodies of three persons collected in Tigoni area of Limuru. 



