Initial scrutiny through close contacts indicated that they were not the ones, although the family planned to travel to Kiambu on Wednesday (today). 

Mr Giteme is a person of interest in the attempted murder of lawyer Kirimi Mbogo and is facing a trial in a different matter that led to the injured lawyer and three witnesses being placed under witness protection agency after expressing threats to their lives. 



